FT  17 NOV 93 / UK Company News: Arjo Wiggins takes Polish stake
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Arjo Wiggins Appleton, the Franco-British paper group, has taken a majority
stake in Nitech, a Polish paper merchant.
The acquisition is in line with Arjo's strategy to develop its activities in
central and eastern Europe in order to maintain its position in the enlarged
European market.
</TEXT>
